divs: Sighting DetailsThe person who took the pictures had a feeling to go outside. She usually has a camera with her and took the first picture. She continued to observe the sky then took the remaining photos. She didn't know what the objects were and sent them to another friend to see what she thought they were. She was exited to have captured an the orbs on camera and the other unidentifed object, which appears to have some form as in a craft.
Summary: person went outside to take photos and observed first pinpoint of light
